# The playwright/ subfolder's package.json (pinning the version) is
# committed so every session installs the same thing — but its
# node_modules and lockfile are large, environment-specific, and
# trivially reinstallable (`pnpm install` from this directory), so they
# stay ignored like any other dependency tree.
playwright/node_modules/
playwright/pnpm-lock.yaml
playwright/package-lock.json
